format:
NOTE:
 

Press the button once to start the awning movement, and the same button again to stop awning movement. Otherwise, power will continue to be applied for 30 seconds from the first press and may cause thermal overload protection to engage. If this happens, the awning will resume normal operation once the motor cools.
